                <div class="wcag-no-grade">
                    <p>‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ú‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ê‡∏≤‡∏ô WCAG 2.1</p>
                    <span class="wcag-score">' . ($saved_score ? number_format($saved_score, 1) : '0.0') . '%</span>
                </div>';
