                <button class="wcag-details-toggle" style="display: none;">‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏î</button>
                <div class="wcag-details" style="display: none;"></div>';
