// ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÇ‡∏û‡∏™‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß ‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏û‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏ó slug ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô ID
function update_existing_posts_slug() {
    $args = array(
        DGA_POST_TYPE_FIELD => 'post',
        DGA_POSTS_PER_PAGE => -1,
        DGA_POST_STATUS_FIELD => DGA_PUBLISH_STATUS
    );
    
    $posts = get_posts($args);
    
    foreach($posts as $post) {
        // ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏û‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏ó slug ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô ID ‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏™‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏à post_title
        wp_update_post(array(
            'ID' => $post->ID,
            'post_name' => $post->ID
        ));
    }
}


