// ‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•
function filter_complaints_by_meta($query) {
    global $pagenow, $typenow;
    
    if ($pagenow == 'edit.php' && $typenow == 'complaint' && is_admin()) {
        $qv = &$query->query_vars;
        
        if (isset($_GET['complaint_type']) && $_GET['complaint_type'] != '') {
            $qv['meta_query'][] = array(
                'key' => '_complaint_type',
