// ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ query ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ó‡∏ò‡∏¥‡πå‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ‡∏î‡∏π‡πÇ‡∏û‡∏™‡∏ï‡πå‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏∞ pending ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ
add_action('pre_get_posts', 'allow_pending_preview_for_privileged_users');

function allow_pending_preview_for_privileged_users($query) {
    // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô main query, frontend ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏•‡πá‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏¥‡∏ô
    if (!is_admin() && $query->is_main_query() && is_user_logged_in()) {
        // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏î‡∏π‡∏û‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ß
        if (isset($_GET['preview']) && $_GET['preview'] === 'true') {
            // ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ò‡∏µ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà 1: ‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö post_id ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å query variable ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÜ
            $post_id = 0;
            
            // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å query variable ‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ê‡∏≤‡∏ô
            if (isset($_GET['p'])) {
                $post_id = absint($_GET['p']);
            } elseif (isset($_GET['page_id'])) {
                $post_id = absint($_GET['page_id']);
            } 
            // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å queried object ‡πÉ‡∏ô permalink ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏ß‡∏¢‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏°
            elseif ($query->get_queried_object_id() > 0) {
                $post_id = $query->get_queried_object_id();
            }
            
            // ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ò‡∏µ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà 2: ‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏Å post_id ‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô 0 ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å post type specific
            if ($post_id === 0) {
                // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö custom post type ‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô
                $post_types = array(
                    'egp', 'news', 'mpeople', 'article', 'pha', 
                    'dgallery', 'department', 'complaint'
                );
                
                foreach($post_types as $type) {
                    $type_id_var = $type . '_id';
                    if (isset($_GET[$type_id_var])) {
                        $post_id = absint($_GET[$type_id_var]);
                        break;
                    }
                    
                    // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å query vars ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà WordPress ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥
                    if ($query->get($type_id_var) > 0) {
                        $post_id = $query->get($type_id_var);
                        break;
                    }
                }
            }
            
            // ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏û‡∏ö post_id ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏î‡∏∂‡∏á‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å queried object
            if ($post_id === 0 && is_singular()) {
                global $post;
                if ($post) {
                    $post_id = $post->ID;
                }
            }
            
            // ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ post_id ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏î‡∏π‡∏û‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ß
            if ($post_id > 0) {
                // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ó‡∏ò‡∏¥‡πå‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ
                $current_user = wp_get_current_user();
                $allowed_roles = array(DGA_ADMIN_ROLE, 'editor', 'author');
                
                // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ó‡∏ò‡∏¥‡πå‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏î‡∏π‡πÇ‡∏û‡∏™‡∏ï‡πå pending
                $has_permission = false;
                foreach ($allowed_roles as $role) {
                    if (in_array($role, $current_user->roles)) {
                        $has_permission = true;
                        break;
                    }
                }
                
                // ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ó‡∏ò‡∏¥‡πå‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏∞ 'pending' ‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÑ‡∏õ‡πÉ‡∏ô query
                if ($has_permission) {
                    $post_status = $query->get(DGA_POST_STATUS_FIELD);
                    if (!$post_status) {
                        $post_status = array(DGA_PUBLISH_STATUS);
                    } elseif (is_string($post_status)) {
                        $post_status = array($post_status);
                    }
                    
                    $post_status[] = 'pending';
                    $query->set(DGA_POST_STATUS_FIELD, $post_status);
                    
                    // ‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∂‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏Å
                    error_log('Pending preview activated for post ID: ' . $post_id);
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

// ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á link preview ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÇ‡∏û‡∏™‡∏ï‡πå‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏∞ pending
add_filter('preview_post_link', 'improve_pending_preview_link', 10, 2);

function improve_pending_preview_link($preview_link, $post) {
    // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡πÇ‡∏û‡∏™‡∏ï‡πå‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏∞ 'pending'
    if ($post && $post->post_status === 'pending') {
        // ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á URL ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö query parameter ‡∏ã‡∏∂‡πà‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å post type
        $post_type = get_post_type($post->ID);
        $preview_link = add_query_arg(
            array(
                DGA_POST_TYPE_FIELD => $post_type,
                'p' => $post->ID,
                'preview' => 'true',
                'pending_preview' => 'true',
            ),
            home_url('/')
        );
    }
    return $preview_link;
}

// ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡πÅ‡∏ñ‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏à‡πâ‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏û‡∏™‡∏ï‡πå‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏∞ pending
